            "chapterTitle": "Benevolent Treatment towards Orphans, Girls, the Weak, the Poor and the Humble Persons",
            "urn": 1602640,
            "body": "<p>Anas (May Allah be pleased with him) reported: The Prophet (\ufdfa) said, \"Whoever supports two girls till they attain maturity, he and I will come on the Day of Resurrection like this\". Messenger of Allah (\ufdfa) joined his fingers illustrating this.<br/><br/><b>[Muslim]</b>.<br/><br/></p>",
